import { BrowserRouter as Router, Routes, Route } from "react-router-dom";
import Layout from "./pages/Layout"; // Layout with the sidebar
import WorkerAdd from "./pages/WorkerAdd"; // Page to add a new worker
import WorkerView from "./pages/WorkerView"; // Page to view workers
import WorkerEdit from "./pages/WorkerEdit"; // Page to edit worker info
import WorkerDelete from "./pages/WorkerDelete"; // Page to delete worker
import PayrollAdd from "./pages/PayrollAdd"; // Page to add a payroll record
import PayrollView from "./pages/PayrollView"; // Page to view payroll records
import PayrollEdit from "./pages/PayrollEdit"; // Page to edit payroll record
import PayrollDelete from "./pages/PayrollDelete"; // Page to delete payroll record
import PayrollGenerateReport from "./pages/PayrollGenerateReport"; // Page to generate a payroll report
import PayrollViewReports from "./pages/PayrollViewReports"; // Page to view past reports
import PayrollExportReport from "./pages/PayrollExportReport"; // Page to export reports
import SettingsConfigure from "./pages/SettingsConfigure"; // Page to configure payroll settings
import SettingsManageTaxes from "./pages/SettingsManageTaxes"; // Page to manage tax rates
import SettingsPaymentPeriods from "./pages/SettingsPaymentPeriods"; // Page to set payment periods
import Logout from "./pages/Logout"; // Page to handle logout

function App() {
  return (
      <Routes>
        <Route path="/" element={<Layout />}>
          {/* Worker Management Routes */}
          <Route path="/worker/add" element={<WorkerAdd />} />
          <Route path="/worker/view" element={<WorkerView />} />
          <Route path="/worker/edit" element={<WorkerEdit />} />
          <Route path="/worker/delete" element={<WorkerDelete />} />

          {/* Payroll Management Routes */}
          <Route path="/payroll/add" element={<PayrollAdd />} />
          <Route path="/payroll/view" element={<PayrollView />} />
          <Route path="/payroll/edit" element={<PayrollEdit />} />
          <Route path="/payroll/delete" element={<PayrollDelete />} />

          {/* Payroll Reports Routes */}
          <Route path="/payroll/generate-report" element={<PayrollGenerateReport />} />
          <Route path="/payroll/view-reports" element={<PayrollViewReports />} />
          <Route path="/payroll/export-report" element={<PayrollExportReport />} />

          {/* Settings Routes */}
          <Route path="/settings/configure" element={<SettingsConfigure />} />
          <Route path="/settings/manage-taxes" element={<SettingsManageTaxes />} />
          <Route path="/settings/payment-periods" element={<SettingsPaymentPeriods />} />
          
          {/* Logout Route */}
          <Route path="/logout" element={<Logout />} />
        </Route>
      </Routes>
  );
}

export default App;
